SQL Functions
Class 5 Functions
CAST: Convert data types.
YEAR: Extract year from a date.
GETDATE: Get current date and time.
DATEPART: Extract part of a date.
DATENAME: Get the name of the date part.
DATEDIFF: Calculate the difference between two dates.
Class 5 Queries
Calculate the day difference between order date and ship date.
Find customer names and discount for orders in the Furniture category with discounts between 10% and 15%.
